### Accuracy by Category

| Category | Test Cases | Correct | Accuracy |
|----------|------------|---------|----------|
| **Clean Messages** | 20 | 20 | 100.0% |
| **Toxic Messages** | 41 | 41 | 100.0% |
| **Unclear Messages** | 5 | 3 | 60.0% |
| **Overall** | 66 | 64 | 97.0% |

### Processing Speed

| Pipeline Stage | Average Time | Success Rate |
|----------------|--------------|--------------|
| **Word Filter** | <1ms | 100% |
| **Embedding** | ~10ms | 95% |
| **Fine-tuned** | ~50ms | 98% |
| **RAG** | ~100ms | 90% |

